OL,6,FPlans to exclude who are under
OL,7,Finvestigation for sexual and violent
OL,8,Foffences will be put to a vote after
OL,9,Fthe February recess, Penny Mordaunt
OL,10,Fhas said.
OL,12,FThe Commons Leader did not provide an
OL,13,Fexact date for the vote, and said she
OL,14,Fwanted MPs to have the time to
OL,15,Fscrutinise the plans.
OL,17,FMPs debated proposals on the issue in
OL,18,FJune, but civil service unions
OL,19,Fcriticised the decision not to hold a
OL,20,Fvote at the time and warned against
OL,21,Fkicking the issue into the long grass.
