OL,4,CMPs arrested for sex offences
OL,6,FCurrently, MPs are only prevented from
OL,7,Fattending the parliamentary estate by
OL,8,Fvoluntary arrangements with their own
OL,9,Fparty whips if they are arrested for
OL,10,Fsex offences.
OL,12,FThe House of Commons Commission
OL,13,Fpublished in December updated
OL,14,Fproposals to establish a formal system
OL,15,Ffor what has become known as a risk-
OL,16,Fbased exclusion process.
OL,18,FThe proposals define the threshold at
OL,19,Fwhich MPs face being banned from the
OL,20,Festate more explicitly than in earlier
OL,21,Fplans as at the point of arrest.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/7
