OL,6,FThis is a lower threshold than the
OL,7,Foriginal proposal to start a risk
OL,8,Fassessment only once an MP is charged
OL,9,Fwith a crime.
OL,11,FUnder the plans, a panel, which is
OL,12,Fexpected to include senior MPs, will
OL,13,Fcarry out a risk assessment based on
OL,14,Finformation from the police alongside
OL,15,Fany existing voluntary arrangements
OL,16,Ffor the MP to stay away from
OL,17,FWestminster.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/7
